Â Â  . â In the Vidal-Quadras Roca report on the management of spent nuclear fuel and radioactive waste and in the SeppÃ€nen report on the safety of nuclear installations, we supported all those amendments that sought to impose stricter safety requirements on the operation of the installations, and on the treatment and storage of radioactive waste.
