Whether or not the principle of these loans is acceptable is another matter.
This is a question, however, which would arise regardless of the amendment currently before us.
It should be noted that the mechanism of loans was introduced in 1977 and at the time covered only Member States.
It was amended in 1994, when the question emerged of the EUâs contributing towards encouraging safety improvements in nuclear installations in third countries, in particular Soviet-designed reactors in former Eastern Bloc countries.
Â Â  . My stance of absolute opposition to the use of nuclear power is well known.
